definitions.definition: The last course of a meal , consisting of fruit, sweet confections etc.
examples: I ordered hummus for a starter, a steak as the main course, and chocolate cake for dessert .
Can I see the dessert menu, please?

definitions.definition: A sweet dish or confection served as the last course of a meal .
examples: Trifle is a favourite dessert of the English, but rivalled by pavlova in Australia and New Zealand.

main_definition: The last course of a meal , consisting of fruit, sweet confections etc.
secondary_definitions: A sweet dish or confection served as the last course of a meal .
